description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Facilities Management assistants (Cleaning / Catering)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hours - as and when required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you want to work flexible hours and choose the shifts that you work, depending on your availability and personal circumstances?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you passionate about cleaning or catering and producing high standards? Do you have a positive attitude towards working with service users?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If yes, why don’t you join our staff bank!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for reliable, enthusiastic and self-motivated Facilities Management Assistants (cleaning / Catering ) to join our staff bank to support the Facilities Services in all of the trusts sites, including offices, hospitals (high secure, medium secure and low secure) and community buildings. We require staff in the following areas;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All areas across Merseyside&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Southport&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Whalley (Clitheroe)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a variety of shifts available shifts between 7am– 8pm, 7 days per week, 365 days per year. There is flexibility on request.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Duties will consist of working in our in-patient wards, communal areas, offices and community sites. As part of the flexible Facilities Management Assistant Team you will also be expected to carry out other duties across Facilities including catering, portering and laundry services. Training will be provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited from flexible individuals who have good communication skills, a positive attitude, and can work on their own initiative and also as part of a team. You will need to demonstrate an understanding of the need to deal with patients and staff in a helpful and supportive manner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous experience of NHS hospital cleaning duties and catering provision working within a mental health environment is desirable but not essential. You must be able to demonstrate an understanding of health and safety in relation to safe working practices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please specify which area/s you are interested in working in on your application.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
